body:
[Midgard Saga](https://midgard-saga.gitbook.io/midgard-saga-whitepaper/) launch a contributors plan globally to help develop the initial stages of the Midgard Saga community and to accelerate Midgard Saga's global expansion.

If you are like us and want to create a better "Play And Earn" game ecosystem, welcome to apply Midgard Saga Contributors Plan.

Midgard Saga is striving to create a high-quality gaming experience, and looks forward to building a high-impact gaming community with you.

## What we need you to do

Including but not limited to (any one of them):

* write or translate Midgard Saga articles;
* Actively build Midgard Saga online or offline communities, and actively communicate and interact in the community;
* Creating promotional video for Midgard Saga;
* Doing re-creation design for Midgard Saga;
* Plan or organize online and offline events;
* Market resource development for Midgard Saga;
* Provide guidance and assistance to new members in community.

## Community Contributors Rewards

Midgard Saga expects you to work proactively, with quantifiable results and expected rewards:

* Get Midgard Saga NFT rewards according to your work;
* Contributors who join early have the opportunity to get additional incentives rewards from the game and platform in the future;
* Resource Sharing;
* Assist contributors with various help needed in the process of growth.

## Recruitment Time

Jun 2, 2022 10:00am - Jul 31, 2022 10:00am  UTC

## How to Apply

* Fill out [Midgard Saga Contributors Plan - Application Form](https://forms.gle/Eb4JPTpg3Avdtprk8);
* After the team evaluates the application form, qualified applicants will be contacted for further communication;
* After approved, you will officially become a Midgard Saga Contributor and work collaboratively with the team.

Midgard Saga looks forward to working with you to expand the influence of Midgard Saga and create a fun gaming community for GameFi users.

To learn more, visit the official platform and follow Midgard Saga on Twitter, Medium, Mirror, Discord, Telegram and etc.

